 Yazi (file manager)

 Navigation
  j/k                      up/down
  l / Enter                open file/dir
  h                        parent directory
  ~                        home
  /                        search
  z                        jump (zoxide)

 Actions
  Space                    select
  d                        delete
  r                        rename
  c                        copy
  x                        cut
  p                        paste
  .                        toggle hidden
  q                        quit
